description: Try our easy to follow Easy Spanish Chicken Paella recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.

recipeInstructions.text: Add peas, capsicum and olives and simmer for 5 minutes or until all liquid is absorbed and rice is cooked. Serve sprinkled with parsley.
